The paper proposes a novel optimizer for Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) and conducts experiments on image categorization datasets. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the convergence analysis and optimization techniques, which suggests the sub-categories cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
